tests.name: increment-bird-no-visits-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Increment today's count with no previous visits" (is (= [6 5 5 11 2 5 1] (bird-watcher/inc-bird [6 5 5 11 2 5 0]))))

tests.name: increment-bird-multiple-visits-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Increment today's count with multiple previous visits" (is (= [5 2 4 2 4 5 8] (bird-watcher/inc-bird [5 2 4 2 4 5 7]))))

tests.message: Expected (= true (bird-watcher/day-without-birds? [5 5 4 0 7 6 7])) but got (not (= true nil))
tests.name: day-without-birds-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Has day without birds with day without birds" (is (= true (bird-watcher/day-without-birds? [5 5 4 0 7 6 7]))))

tests.message: Expected (= false (bird-watcher/day-without-birds? [5 5 4 1 7 6 7])) but got (not (= false nil))
tests.name: no-day-without-birds-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Has day without birds with no day without birds" (is (= false (bird-watcher/day-without-birds? [5 5 4 1 7 6 7]))))

tests.name: n-days-count-disappointing-week-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Count for first three days of disappointing week" (is (= 1 (bird-watcher/n-days-count [0 0 1 0 0 1 0] 3))))

tests.name: n-days-count-busy-week-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Count for first 6 days of busy week" (is (= 48 (bird-watcher/n-days-count [5 9 12 6 8 8 17] 6))))

tests.message: Expected (= true (bird-watcher/odd-week? [1 0 1 0 1 0 1])) but got (not (= true nil))
tests.name: odd-week-matching-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Odd week for week matching odd pattern" (is (= true (bird-watcher/odd-week? [1 0 1 0 1 0 1]))))

tests.message: Expected (= false (bird-watcher/odd-week? [2 2 1 0 1 1 1])) but got (not (= false nil))
tests.name: odd-week-not-matching-test
tests.test_code: (testing "Odd week for week that does not match pattern" (is (= false (bird-watcher/odd-week? [2 2 1 0 1 1 1]))))
